metatags.og:title: The false tale of the bullfighter’s epiphany
metatags.og:description: A photo of a matador facing a bull has recently resurfaced and is presented as the exact moment that led Alvaro Munera to end his bullfighting career, upon realizing the cruelty of his sport. However, the real Munera ended his career after a severe injury, and the matador in the photo is intentionally striking a dangerous pose to challenge the bull.
